          </div>
          <div class="review-content">
            <div class="review-text">
              Over the past four years, I have engaged in multiple projects with Precious Infosystem, and I am thoroughly delighted with their contributions. They consistently address any queries that arise promptly, embodying a team that adeptly transforms my ideas into reality. I couldn't envision a more capable and responsive team to collaborate with.
            </div>
            <div class="reviewer-name">John Smith</div>
            <!-- <div class="reviewer-post">CEO, Founder of XYZ</div> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item d-flex gap-3 align-items-center position-relative">
          <div class="review-img">
            <%= image_tag 'theme1/testimonial2.jpg' ,class: "reviewer-img" , alt: '' %>
          </div>
          <div class="review-content">
            <div class="review-text">
              I have consistently found Precious Infosystem to be a dependable collaborator in my website development endeavors. Their responsiveness to my requests has been impressive, and their technical proficiency has remained consistently impressive over the course of our partnership.
            </div>
