            <!-- <div class="reviewer-post">CEO, Founder of XYZ</div> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item d-flex gap-3 align-items-center position-relative">
          <div class="review-img">
            <%= image_tag 'theme1/testimonial3.jpg' ,class: "reviewer-img" , alt: '' %>
          </div>
          <div class="review-content">
            <div class="review-text">
              Working with the Precious Infosystem was a delightful experience. They exhibited responsiveness, clear communication, and a genuine willingness to engage with all facets of the project. Their diligent efforts and evident sense of pride in their work were truly commendable.
